{
  "texts": [
    "Pharmaceuticals are often stolen from the supply chain and sold illegally to various customers.",
    "Furthermore, counterfeit pharmaceuticals alone cost these businesses roughly $200 billion every year.",
    "A transparent blockchain will assist these firms in enabling close tracking of medications back to their place of origin, Research on consensus algorithms has been a prevalent topic for the past 30 years, even before the creation of blockchain technology.",
    "Reference [48] give a summary of some of the early work in distributed systems consensus.",
    "Consensus algorithms play a vital role in the functioning of blockchain technology."
  ]
}